# ElbyCDIO.sys ![:inline](/images/twitter_verified.png) 

### Description

ElbyCDIO.sys is a vulnerable driver and more information will be added as found.
- **UUID**: 7a722cd5-69ec-4680-9f20-9387f249a891
- **Created**: 2023-05-06
- **Author**: Nasreddine Bencherchali
- **Acknowledgement**:  | [](https://twitter.com/)

{{< tip "warning" >}}
This download link contains the vulnerable driver!

{{< /tip >}}

### Commands

```
sc.exe create ElbyCDIO.sys binPath=C:\windows\temp\ElbyCDIO.sys type=kernel &amp;&amp; sc.exe start ElbyCDIO.sys
```


| Use Case | Privileges | Operating System | 
|:---- | ---- | ---- |
| Elevate privileges | kernel | Windows 10 |
